niques. In the context of feature\nselection, CIPLS achieves comparable results when compared to state-of-the-art\ntechniques.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 5 Oct 2019 19:45:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 10 Nov 2020 14:23:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-11"}
