, Waymo) to understand the values of AVs, especially the values of\nmassive data collected by AVs, in traffic operation and management.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 6 Oct 2019 05:07:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-08"}
